{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":838,"text":"In the past several days, I heard people talking about China."},{"time":5449,"text":"And also, I talked to friends about China and Chinese Internet."},{"time":9403,"text":"Something is very challenging to me."},{"time":11866,"text":"I want to make my friends understand:"},{"time":14927,"text":"China is complicated."},{"time":18495,"text":"So I always want to tell the story, like,"},{"time":20590,"text":"one hand it is that, the other hand is that."},{"time":24046,"text":"You can't just tell a one sided story."},{"time":26832,"text":"I'll give an example. China is a BRIC country."},{"time":30013,"text":"BRIC country means Brazil, Russia, India and China."},{"time":35423,"text":"This emerging economy really is helping the revival of the world economy."},{"time":41249,"text":"But at the same time, on the other hand,"},{"time":44418,"text":"China is a SICK country,"},{"time":47322,"text":"the terminology coined by Facebook IPO papers -- file."},{"time":53278,"text":"He said the SICK country means Syria, Iran, China and North Korea."},{"time":59560,"text":"The four countries have no access to Facebook."},{"time":64240,"text":"So basically, China is a SICK BRIC country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68358,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":69352,"text":"Another project was built up"},{"time":71247,"text":"to watch China and Chinese Internet."},{"time":74091,"text":"And now, today I want to tell you my personal"},{"time":77474,"text":"observation in the past several years, from that wall."},{"time":82706,"text":"So, if you are a fan of the Game of Thrones,"},{"time":86267,"text":"you definitely know how important a big wall is for an old kingdom."},{"time":91250,"text":"It prevents weird things from the north."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96126,"text":"Same was true for China."},{"time":99323,"text":"In the north, there was a great wall, Chang Cheng."},{"time":102883,"text":"It protected China from invaders for 2,000 years."},{"time":108255,"text":"But China also has a great firewall."},{"time":112318,"text":"That's the biggest digital boundary in the whole world."},{"time":116647,"text":"It's not only to defend the Chinese regime from overseas,"},{"time":120972,"text":"from the universal values, but also to prevent"},{"time":124676,"text":"China's own citizens to access the global free Internet,"},{"time":128351,"text":"and even separate themselves into blocks, not united."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133639,"text":"So, basically the \"Internet\" has two Internets."},{"time":137785,"text":"One is the Internet, the other is the Chinanet."},{"time":141777,"text":"But if you think the Chinanet is something"},{"time":145569,"text":"like a deadland, wasteland, I think it's wrong."},{"time":152091,"text":"But we also use a very simple metaphor, the cat and the mouse game,"},{"time":157828,"text":"to describe in the past 15 years"},{"time":160851,"text":"the continuing fight between Chinese"},{"time":164251,"text":"censorship, government censorship, the cat,"},{"time":167531,"text":"and the Chinese Internet users. That means us, the mouse."},{"time":173683,"text":"But sometimes this kind of a metaphor is too simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177876,"text":"So today I want to upgrade it to 2.0 version."},{"time":183311,"text":"In China, we have 500 million Internet users."},{"time":187073,"text":"That's the biggest population of Netizens, Internet users, in the whole world."},{"time":191928,"text":"So even though China's is a totally censored Internet,"},{"time":197439,"text":"but still, Chinese Internet society is really booming."},{"time":201033,"text":"How to make it? It's simple."},{"time":203743,"text":"You have Google, we have Baidu."},{"time":206444,"text":"You have Twitter, we have Weibo."},{"time":209558,"text":"You have Facebook, we have Renren."},{"time":212583,"text":"You have YouTube, we have Youku and Tudou."},{"time":217916,"text":"The Chinese government blocked every"},{"time":222446,"text":"single international Web 2.0 service,"},{"time":226157,"text":"and we Chinese copycat every one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228973,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":230366,"text":"So, that's the kind of the thing I call smart censorship."},{"time":234981,"text":"That's not only to censor you."},{"time":238549,"text":"Sometimes this Chinese national Internet policy is very simple:"},{"time":243148,"text":"Block and clone."},{"time":245535,"text":"On the one hand, he wants to satisfy people's need of a social network,"},{"time":250639,"text":"which is very important; people really love social networking."},{"time":253919,"text":"But on the other hand, they want to keep the server"},{"time":256744,"text":"in Beijing so they can access the data any time they want."},{"time":261274,"text":"That's also the reason Google was pulled out from China,"},{"time":265522,"text":"because they can't accept the fact"},{"time":267331,"text":"that Chinese government wants to keep the server."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272130,"text":"Sometimes the Arab dictators didn't understand these two hands."},{"time":277558,"text":"For example, Mubarak, he shut down the Internet."},{"time":281311,"text":"He wanted to prevent the Netizens [from criticizing] him."},{"time":284423,"text":"But once Netizens can't go online, they go in the street."},{"time":290113,"text":"And now the result is very simple."},{"time":293393,"text":"We all know Mubarak is technically dead."},{"time":299003,"text":"But also, Ben Ali, Tunisian president,"},{"time":303515,"text":"didn't follow the second rule."},{"time":305441,"text":"That means keep the server in your hands."},{"time":309394,"text":"He allowed Facebook, a U.S.-based service,"},{"time":315239,"text":"to continue to stay on inside of Tunisia."},{"time":318641,"text":"So he can't prevent it, his own citizens to post"},{"time":322213,"text":"critical videos against his corruption."},{"time":324865,"text":"The same thing happend. He was the first"},{"time":328914,"text":"to topple during the Arab Spring."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331931,"text":"But those two very smart international censorship policies"},{"time":337081,"text":"didn't prevent Chinese social media [from] becoming a really public sphere,"},{"time":343418,"text":"a pathway of public opinion and the nightmare of Chinese officials."},{"time":349091,"text":"Because we have 300 million microbloggers in China."},{"time":353619,"text":"It's the entire population of the United States."},{"time":357451,"text":"So when these 300 million people, microbloggers,"},{"time":361315,"text":"even they block the tweet in our censored platform."},{"time":366083,"text":"But itself -- the Chinanet -- but itself can create"},{"time":370070,"text":"very powerful energy, which has never happened"},{"time":374165,"text":"in the Chinese history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375819,"text":"2011, in July, two [unclear] trains crashed,"},{"time":380515,"text":"in Wenzhou, a southern city."},{"time":382771,"text":"Right after the train crash,"},{"time":384395,"text":"authorities literally wanted to cover up the train, bury the train."},{"time":389411,"text":"So it angered the Chinese Netizens."},{"time":391627,"text":"The first five days after the train crash,"},{"time":394690,"text":"there were 10 million criticisms of the posting"},{"time":398835,"text":"on social media, which never happened in Chinese history."},{"time":402588,"text":"And later this year, the rail minister"},{"time":405916,"text":"was sacked and sentenced to jail for 10 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411382,"text":"And also, recently, very funny debate between"},{"time":416429,"text":"the Beijing Environment Ministry"},{"time":419725,"text":"and the American Embassy in Beijing"},{"time":423093,"text":"because the Ministry blamed"},{"time":425558,"text":"the American Embassy for intervening in"},{"time":427703,"text":"Chinese internal politics by disclosing"},{"time":431132,"text":"the air quality data of Beijing."},{"time":433816,"text":"So, the up is the Embassy data, the PM 2.5."},{"time":440704,"text":"He showed 148, they showed it's dangerous for the sensitive group."},{"time":446648,"text":"So a suggestion, it's not good to go outside."},{"time":450450,"text":"But that is the Ministry's data. He shows 50."},{"time":456074,"text":"He says it's good. It's good to go outside."},{"time":459426,"text":"But 99 percent of Chinese microbloggers"},{"time":462970,"text":"stand firmly on the Embassy's side."},{"time":466730,"text":"I live in Beijing. Every day, I just watch"},{"time":471402,"text":"the American Embassy's data to decide whether I should open my window."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480133,"text":"Why is Chinese social networking, even within the censorship,"},{"time":484424,"text":"so booming? Part of the reason is Chinese languages."},{"time":488668,"text":"You know, Twitter and Twitter clones have a kind of"},{"time":492340,"text":"a limitation of 140 characters."},{"time":494805,"text":"But in English it's 20 words or a sentence with a short link."},{"time":499004,"text":"Maybe in Germany, in German language, it may be just \"Aha!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":502252,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":504786,"text":"But in Chinese language, it's really about 140 characters,"},{"time":510531,"text":"means a paragraph, a story."},{"time":513207,"text":"You can almost have all the journalistic elements there."},{"time":517445,"text":"For example, this is Hamlet, of Shakespeare."},{"time":521132,"text":"It's the same content. One, you can see exactly"},{"time":524923,"text":"one Chinese tweet is equal to 3.5 English tweets."},{"time":531436,"text":"Chinese is always cheating, right?"},{"time":534693,"text":"So because of this, the Chinese really regard this"},{"time":538606,"text":"microblogging as a media, not only a headline to media."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543687,"text":"And also, the clone, Sina company is"},{"time":547398,"text":"the guy who cloned Twitter."},{"time":549485,"text":"It even has its own name, with Weibo."},{"time":551906,"text":"\"Weibo\" is the Chinese translation for \"microblog\"."},{"time":554341,"text":"It has its own innovation."},{"time":556245,"text":"At the commenting area, [it makes] the Chinese Weibo"},{"time":559878,"text":"more like Facebook, rather than the original Twitter."},{"time":563620,"text":"So these innovations and clones, as the Weibo and microblogging,"},{"time":568044,"text":"when it came to China in 2009,"},{"time":570364,"text":"it immediately became a media platform itself."},{"time":574377,"text":"It became the media platform of 300 million readers."},{"time":578578,"text":"It became the media."},{"time":580479,"text":"Anything not mentioned in Weibo,"},{"time":582904,"text":"it does not appear to exist for the Chinese public."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588188,"text":"But also, Chinese social media is"},{"time":590624,"text":"really changing Chinese mindsets and Chinese life."},{"time":595019,"text":"For example, they give the voiceless people"},{"time":598508,"text":"a channel to make your voice heard."},{"time":601261,"text":"We had a petition system. It's a remedy outside the judicial system,"},{"time":606704,"text":"because the Chinese central government wants to keep a myth:"},{"time":609781,"text":"The emperor is good. The old local officials are thugs."},{"time":614407,"text":"So that's why the petitioner, the victims, the peasants,"},{"time":617798,"text":"want to take the train to Beijing to petition to the central government,"},{"time":621429,"text":"they want the emperor to settle the problem."},{"time":624224,"text":"But when more and more people go to Beijing,"},{"time":627063,"text":"they also cause the risk of a revolution."},{"time":630586,"text":"So they send them back in recent years."},{"time":633458,"text":"And even some of them were put into black jails."},{"time":637025,"text":"But now we have Weibo, so I call it the Weibo petition."},{"time":640626,"text":"People just use their cell phones to tweet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643465,"text":"So your sad stories, by some chance your story"},{"time":647042,"text":"will be picked up by reporters, professors or celebrities."},{"time":650683,"text":"One of them is Yao Chen,"},{"time":652596,"text":"she is the most popular microblogger in China,"},{"time":655985,"text":"who has about 21 million followers."},{"time":659844,"text":"They're almost like a national TV station."},{"time":663466,"text":"If you -- so a sad story will be picked up by her."},{"time":666802,"text":"So this Weibo social media, even in the censorship,"},{"time":671250,"text":"still gave the Chinese a real chance for 300 million people"},{"time":676990,"text":"every day chatting together, talking together."},{"time":680314,"text":"It's like a big TED, right?"},{"time":683220,"text":"But also, it is like the first time a public sphere"},{"time":687068,"text":"happened in China."},{"time":688772,"text":"Chinese people start to learn how to negotiate"},{"time":691987,"text":"and talk to people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695172,"text":"But also, the cat, the censorship, is not sleeping."},{"time":698876,"text":"It's so hard to post some sensitive words on the Chinese Weibo."},{"time":703122,"text":"For example, you can't post the name of the president,"},{"time":706329,"text":"Hu Jintao, and also you can't post the city of Chongqing, the name,"},{"time":711907,"text":"and until recently, you can't search the surname of top leaders."},{"time":716641,"text":"So, the Chinese are very good at these puns"},{"time":720974,"text":"and alternative wording and even memes."},{"time":724646,"text":"They even name themselves -- you know,"},{"time":726891,"text":"use the name of this world-changing"},{"time":729386,"text":"battle between the grass-mud horse and the river crab."},{"time":733357,"text":"The grass-mud horse is caoníma,"},{"time":735366,"text":"is the phonogram for motherfucker,"},{"time":738320,"text":"the Netizens call themselves."},{"time":744536,"text":"River crab is héxiè, is the phonogram for"},{"time":747153,"text":"harmonization, for censorship."},{"time":750047,"text":"So that's kind of a caoníma versus the héxiè, that's very good."},{"time":755167,"text":"So, when some very political, exciting moments happened,"},{"time":761144,"text":"you can see on Weibo, you see a lot of very weird stories happened."},{"time":766725,"text":"Weird phrases and words, even if you have a PhD"},{"time":771557,"text":"of Chinese language, you can't understand them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775024,"text":"But you can't even expand more, no, because"},{"time":777847,"text":"Chinese Sina Weibo, when it was founded"},{"time":780770,"text":"was exactly one month after the official blocking of Twitter.com."},{"time":785906,"text":"That means from the very beginning,"},{"time":788002,"text":"Weibo has already convinced the Chinese government,"},{"time":792194,"text":"we will not become the stage for"},{"time":794938,"text":"any kind of a threat to the regime."},{"time":797530,"text":"For example, anything you want to post,"},{"time":799730,"text":"like \"get together\" or \"meet up\" or \"walk,\""},{"time":802625,"text":"it is automatically recorded and data mined"},{"time":806818,"text":"and reported to a poll for further political analyzing."},{"time":813346,"text":"Even if you want to have some gathering,"},{"time":815346,"text":"before you go there, the police are already waiting for you."},{"time":819026,"text":"Why? Because they have the data."},{"time":820834,"text":"They have everything in their hands."},{"time":823026,"text":"So they can use the 1984 scenario data mining of the dissident."},{"time":829250,"text":"So the crackdown is very serious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832849,"text":"But I want you to notice a very funny thing"},{"time":835390,"text":"during the process of the cat-and-mouse."},{"time":838278,"text":"The cat is the censorship, but Chinese is not only one cat,"},{"time":842503,"text":"but also has local cats. Central cat and local cats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846131,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":848057,"text":"You know, the server is in the [central] cats' hands,"},{"time":851131,"text":"so even that -- when the Netizens criticize the local government,"},{"time":855753,"text":"the local government has not any access to the data in Beijing."},{"time":860391,"text":"Without bribing the central cats,"},{"time":862279,"text":"he can do nothing, only apologize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":865705,"text":"So these three years, in the past three years,"},{"time":868433,"text":"social movements about microblogging"},{"time":871079,"text":"really changed local government,"},{"time":873440,"text":"became more and more transparent,"},{"time":875696,"text":"because they can't access the data."},{"time":878544,"text":"The server is in Beijing."},{"time":882157,"text":"The story about the train crash,"},{"time":883627,"text":"maybe the question is not about why 10 million"},{"time":886834,"text":"criticisms in five days, but why the Chinese central government"},{"time":891080,"text":"allowed the five days of freedom of speech online."},{"time":894304,"text":"It's never happened before."},{"time":896213,"text":"And so it's very simple, because even the top leaders"},{"time":899664,"text":"were fed up with this guy, this independent kingdom."},{"time":903185,"text":"So they want an excuse --"},{"time":904855,"text":"public opinion is a very good excuse to punish him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":908312,"text":"But also, the Bo Xilai case recently, very big news,"},{"time":911282,"text":"he's a princeling."},{"time":912613,"text":"But from February to April this year,"},{"time":916732,"text":"Weibo really became a marketplace of rumors."},{"time":919435,"text":"You can almost joke everything about these princelings,"},{"time":922772,"text":"everything! It's almost like you're living in the United States."},{"time":926172,"text":"But if you dare to retweet or mention any fake coup"},{"time":930821,"text":"about Beijing, you definitely will be arrested."},{"time":934764,"text":"So this kind of freedom is a targeted and precise window."}]},{"cues":[{"time":940687,"text":"So Chinese in China, censorship is normal."},{"time":944556,"text":"Something you find is, freedom is weird."},{"time":947301,"text":"Something will happen behind it."},{"time":949068,"text":"Because he was a very popular Leftist leader,"},{"time":952224,"text":"so the central government wanted to purge him,"},{"time":954428,"text":"and he was very cute, he convinced all the Chinese people,"},{"time":958510,"text":"why he is so bad."},{"time":960340,"text":"So Weibo, the 300 million public sphere,"},{"time":964118,"text":"became a very good, convenient tool for a political fight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968629,"text":"But this technology is very new,"},{"time":970786,"text":"but technically is very old."},{"time":972452,"text":"It was made famous by Chairman Mao, Mao Zedong,"},{"time":975380,"text":"because he mobilized millions of Chinese people"},{"time":978277,"text":"in the Cultural Revolution to destroy every local government."},{"time":982359,"text":"It's very simple, because Chinese central government"},{"time":985229,"text":"doesn't need to even lead the public opinion."},{"time":987365,"text":"They just give them a target window to not censor people."},{"time":991896,"text":"Not censoring in China has become a political tool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":997805,"text":"So that's the update about this game, cat-and-mouse."},{"time":1001775,"text":"Social media changed Chinese mindset."},{"time":1003945,"text":"More and more Chinese intend to embrace freedom of speech"},{"time":1007455,"text":"and human rights as their birthright,"},{"time":1009615,"text":"not some imported American privilege."},{"time":1013237,"text":"But also, it gave the Chinese a national public sphere"},{"time":1016949,"text":"for people to, it's like a training of their citizenship,"},{"time":1021279,"text":"preparing for future democracy."},{"time":1023850,"text":"But it didn't change the Chinese political system,"},{"time":1026306,"text":"and also the Chinese central government utilized this"},{"time":1029551,"text":"centralized server structure to strengthen its power"},{"time":1033487,"text":"to counter the local government and the different factions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1037985,"text":"So, what's the future?"},{"time":1040757,"text":"After all, we are the mouse."},{"time":1042941,"text":"Whatever the future is, we should fight against the [cat]."},{"time":1046741,"text":"There is not only in China, but also in the United States"},{"time":1050732,"text":"there are some very small, cute but bad cats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1055561,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1057205,"text":"SOPA, PIPA, ACTA, TPP and ITU."},{"time":1063943,"text":"And also, like Facebook and Google, they claim they are friends of the mouse,"},{"time":1069298,"text":"but sometimes we see them dating the cats."},{"time":1073485,"text":"So my conclusion is very simple."},{"time":1076669,"text":"We Chinese fight for our freedom,"},{"time":1079514,"text":"you just watch your bad cats."},{"time":1083109,"text":"Don't let them hook [up] with the Chinese cats."},{"time":1086012,"text":"Only in this way, in the future,"},{"time":1088853,"text":"we will achieve the dreams of the mouse:"},{"time":1092101,"text":"that we can tweet anytime, anywhere, without fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1096077,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1103436,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1105121,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}